    "\"A Metaverse: Taxonomy, Components, Applications, and Open Challenges\", by Park and Kim (2022), with eight citations.",
    "This paper studies the necessary components to build the Metaverse (hardware, software and contents well organized to maintain the experience) and investigates its limitations and potential issues.",
